mission.gis: Armed with Throwing Knives and Shotguns, run explosives into the enemy's base. Destroy it before they destroy yours.
md: Special edition of Up in Smoke: teams run explosives into each
other's territory, while preventing other teams from doing the
same, all with Throwing Knives and Shotguns as their only weapo
ns. Enemy players will not be shown on the radar.~n~~n~2 Teams~
